  <entry>
    <title>C++对外发布api</title>
    <link href="https://iyux.github.io/2021/04/15/C-%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83api/"/>
    <id>https://iyux.github.io/2021/04/15/C-%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83api/</id>
    <published>2021-04-15T08:20:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-04-15T08:27:32.543Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="C的api实现"><a href="#C的api实现" class="headerlink" title="C的api实现"></a>C的api实现</h1><h2 id="大致流程"><a href="#大致流程" class="headerlink" title="大致流程"></a>大致流程</h2><p>从前都是写的C的api，大概流程是做一个void* 的指针，我们把他称之为句柄</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> XXX_HANDEL void*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//or</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">void</span>* XXX_HANDLE</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//对外的api (interface.h)暴露出公开的函数，形式一般为</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">XXX_HANDLE <span class="title">init</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">release</span><span class="params">(XXX_HANDLE handle)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">func</span><span class="params">(HANDEL handle, <span class="keyword">int</span> param)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//...</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在内部头文件中，定义handle的结构体，再对handle的结构体进行转换，这样对外屏蔽了指针的内部实现。函数围绕句柄指针来进行使用</p><h2 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h2><p>在纯c的api里，若要让外部c++进行调用，要进行extern “c”的说明</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">ifdef</span> __cplusplus</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">extern</span> <span class="string">&quot;c&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">endif</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// ...</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">ifdef</span> __cplusplus</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>原因是C++与C对函数名在编译时进行的名字扩展不同，不加入extern “c”，会在链接时产生函数未定义的错误</p><p>另外句柄的实现和销毁时，要进行内存的管理</p><h1 id="C-的api实现"><a href="#C-的api实现" class="headerlink" title="C++的api实现"></a>C++的api实现</h1><h2 id="大致流程-1"><a href="#大致流程-1" class="headerlink" title="大致流程"></a>大致流程</h2><p>采用对象的形式使程序结构更加清晰，对象的构建与销毁使内存管理更加直观与便捷。<br>采用C++里类的结构，一般来说，这样会暴露类里的私有成员，但是可以通过纯虚函数的形式去定义接口，包含纯虚函数的雷不能实例化对象，但是可以通过指针调用。</p><p>方式：设计公开的基类，包含需要对外开放的纯虚函数成员，在内部实现中，子类继承基类，并添加仅内部可见的私有成员，并对各个函数做具体实现，返回子类对象的指针。</p><p>返回指针的方式有两种<br>1.在接口定义中使用独立的函数返回积累的指针<br>2.在基类的成员函数中添加一个返回值为该基类指针的非虚函数</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//interface.hpp 对外接口</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&quot;stdio.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">testA</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">testA *<span class="title">init</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">testA</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">virtual</span> ~<span class="built_in">testA</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">fun1</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">fun2</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//或者采用单独函数返回对象指针</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">testA* <span class="title">initTestA</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//inner_interface.hpp 内部定义</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&quot;interface.hpp&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">testB</span> :</span><span class="keyword">public</span> testA&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">testB</span> ();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">virtual</span> ~<span class="built_in">testB</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">fun1</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">virtual</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">fun2</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> aaa;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//具体实现</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&quot;inner_interface.hpp&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">testA::<span class="built_in">testA</span>()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;A build\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">testA::~<span class="built_in">testA</span>()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">testA* <span class="title">testA::init</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    testB *b = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">testB</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> b;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">testB::<span class="built_in">testB</span>()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;B build\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">testA::fun1</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// aaa = k;</span></span><br><span class="line">    ;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">testA::fun2</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// printf(&quot;private value = %d\n&quot;, aaa);</span></span><br><span class="line">    ;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">testB::fun1</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    aaa = k;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">testB::fun2</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;private value = %d\n&quot;</span>, aaa);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">testB::~<span class="built_in">testB</span>()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//main.cpp</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&quot;interface.hpp&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    testA* ptr = <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    ptr = ptr-&gt;<span class="built_in">init</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    ptr-&gt;<span class="built_in">fun1</span>(<span class="number">100</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    ptr-&gt;<span class="built_in">fun2</span>();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对外发布interface.hpp与相应的动态库即可</p><h2 id="补充"><a href="#补充" class="headerlink" title="补充"></a>补充</h2><p>1.纯虚函数也可以进行实现(理论上的不行的)，意义是对子类的该方法的缺省实现<br>2.对于如下表达</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">testA* ptr = <span class="literal">nullptr</span>;</span><br><span class="line">ptr = ptr -&gt; <span class="built_in">init</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在对象调用函数的流程中，方法被实际展开为<br>func(obj, p1, p2, …)<br>即使prt为空指针，函数依然能够调用(函数存在代码区)，只要该函数没有设计到对象实际存储成员的使用，就不会产生问题。<br>验证:</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//基类加入 新成员 int bbb;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//init() 中对bbb进行赋值 bbb=0;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>产生segment fault<br>对bbb赋值时  obj-&gt;bbb=0，而obj = nullptr，产生错误</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
